        <abstract> 
<p>Is sick of hostile reviews but they have helped in showing where he must expatiate and expand in new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Has more confidence in the general truth of his view. Disappointed THH does not think it more probable than he did at first.</p>
        </abstract>
